description:
The Beside Table is a low side table with a deep storage shelf. Two tables can
be milled from a single 4’x8’ sheet, with each comprised of 11 flat,
interlocking pieces that are easily constructed and secured with screws, pegs or
adhesives.

A pair of tables can be constructed from a single 4’x8’ sheet of material. The
Beside Table can be accessorised with a 3D printed Peg & Foot Kit, which can be
found at AtFAB's [Thingiverse page][].

[Thingiverse page]: http://www.thingiverse.com/atfab
